## When Stuck

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| Element not found | Verify data-testid exists, check for typos |
| Test flaky | Run with `--trace=on`, find timing issue |
| Database state wrong | Check cleanup, verify seed data |
| Test too slow | Consider if E2E is appropriate scope |
| Can't select element | Add data-testid to component |

## Final Rule

```
E2E test → uses data-testid, independent, deterministic
Otherwise → fix before committing
```

No exceptions without human partner's permission.

